{"tid":124053,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"七警聞判囚後嘆氣　第二被告更飲泣","createTime":"2017-02-17T09:41:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-17T13:06:29.000Z","uid":408,"like":70,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f10443740cd0691ec685c1385af68795dcf72950","tid":124053,"uid":408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T09:41:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170217/bkn-20170217131403002-0217_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170217%2Fbkn-20170217131403002-0217_00822_001.html&d=qLBezvvtP0%2Ff8NIwCarvwiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=3d0cd917\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170217/bkn-20170217131403002-0217_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n7名警務人員於2014年10月佔領運動期間，在金鐘龍匯道的變電站旁毆打前公民黨成員曾健超，7名警員被裁定襲擊致造成身體受傷的交替控罪罪成，而第5被告陳少丹普通襲擊罪亦罪成。7名被告今早由囚車押解到區域法院聽取判刑。他們依舊穿着同一款整齊西裝應訊，惟經過了三晚還押後，7人均顯得相當憔悴及疲倦，不時呆望及閉目休息。<br />\n<br />\n多名被告在庭上獲悉須監禁兩年後嘆氣，其中第二被告劉卓毅更飲泣起來，又說出一句「幫我照顧屋企人」。散庭時亦有部分被告親友上前走近犯人欄爭取與被告見面，但沒機會交談，其後眾被告則進入拘留室。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"744d5b3d60db6e368952edbe68a4ca634d137e3e","tid":124053,"uid":408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T09:42:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96b4880e402eac3294b250a6bd684d149b79708d","tid":124053,"uid":129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T09:42:56.000Z","msg":"抵啦"},{"pid":"2711341ffa55572991b0b153880cbb0dc94d1080","tid":124053,"uid":49279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T09:42:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ziines.com/ziines-user-upload/upload/2016/03/10/1687_20160310161600_56e12d40c3081.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ziines.com%2